    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-06-11</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-07-13T14:17:01Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Recycling Investment Saves Energy or the RISE Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow: (1) a first-year tax deduction of 50% of the adjusted basis of qualified reuse and recycling property; and (2) tax-exempt bond financing for recycling facilities. Defines &quot;qualified reuse and recycling property&quot; as property placed in service after December 31, 2006, which has a useful life of at least five years and which is used exclusively to collect, distribute, or recycle certain scrap materials.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
